WEBVTT

00:00:07.725 --> 00:00:11.711
♪I found a faint light
in the fading dusk♪

00:00:11.712 --> 00:00:15.311
♪And met your steady gaze♪

00:00:15.312 --> 00:00:24.132
♪One knowing glance,
and side by side we walk on♪

00:00:24.575 --> 00:00:27.061
♪Longing finds no place to rest♪

00:00:27.062 --> 00:00:29.211
♪Through drifting wind and rain♪

00:00:29.212 --> 00:00:32.699
♪You are the prayer within my hands♪

00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:40.324
♪A single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows♪

00:00:40.325 --> 00:00:42.786
♪We made a promise long ago♪

00:00:42.787 --> 00:00:44.786
♪For all our days to come♪

00:00:44.787 --> 00:00:48.449
♪You are the fate I cannot outrun♪

00:00:48.450 --> 00:00:53.836
♪How much must I let go
to trade for one moment?♪

00:00:53.837 --> 00:00:56.457
♪Holding you close♪

00:00:56.637 --> 00:00:58.874
♪Would that be enough?♪

00:00:58.875 --> 00:00:59.579
=Echoes of Love=

00:00:59.580 --> 00:01:01.499
(Adapted from the signed screenplay
Echoes of Love on Migu Reading)

00:01:01.500 --> 00:01:03.649
=Episode 22=

00:01:03.650 --> 00:01:09.070
(Gu Residence)

00:01:10.350 --> 00:01:14.932
(Gu Residence)

00:01:16.737 --> 00:01:20.820
(Wanted Poster)

00:01:29.859 --> 00:01:31.900
We're currently wanted
throughout the city,

00:01:31.979 --> 00:01:33.459
so we can't enter the palace.

00:01:33.900 --> 00:01:35.559
The evidence from
the Court of Judicial Review

00:01:35.559 --> 00:01:37.700
can only shut down
Huanyue House and Shengtang Guild.

00:01:37.700 --> 00:01:40.220
It isn't enough to bring Gao Deng
and Dowager Consort Wu to justice.

00:01:47.180 --> 00:01:49.379
Next month is
Dowager Consort Wu's birthday.

00:01:49.380 --> 00:01:51.320
Every year, she organizes
female folk performers

00:01:51.320 --> 00:01:53.120
to showcase their talents
before His Majesty,

00:01:53.259 --> 00:01:55.780
to show the royal family
sharing joy with the commoners.

00:01:56.779 --> 00:01:58.379
Now that the scandal of Shengtang Guild

00:01:58.380 --> 00:01:59.700
has caused such a stir,

00:02:01.125 --> 00:02:03.498
Dowager Consort Wu
will surely use this birthday banquet

00:02:03.499 --> 00:02:05.099
to mend her relationship
with His Majesty.

00:02:05.100 --> 00:02:06.620
This might be

00:02:06.779 --> 00:02:08.220
our last chance.

00:02:11.180 --> 00:02:12.900
But we have to find a way.

00:02:13.900 --> 00:02:15.419
The birthday banquet will definitely be

00:02:16.180 --> 00:02:17.780
heavily guarded.

00:02:22.460 --> 00:02:23.259
Right.

00:02:24.100 --> 00:02:26.399
We can use the performance
as a way to sneak in

00:02:26.400 --> 00:02:28.240
and present the evidence
directly to His Majesty.

00:02:36.300 --> 00:02:37.419
Mother,

00:02:38.099 --> 00:02:39.020
I wish you

00:02:39.260 --> 00:02:40.859
eternal youth and vitality,

00:02:40.860 --> 00:02:42.179
everlasting health,

00:02:42.180 --> 00:02:43.778
joy year after year,

00:02:43.779 --> 00:02:45.538
and lasting prosperity.

00:02:45.539 --> 00:02:47.099
Thank you, Your Majesty.

00:02:47.980 --> 00:02:51.538
Bring in the performers
from Shengtang Guild

00:02:51.539 --> 00:02:54.820
to celebrate
the Dowager Consort's birthday.

00:03:07.539 --> 00:03:09.859
Regarding this year's performances,

00:03:09.860 --> 00:03:12.259
what do you think, Your Majesty?

00:03:12.779 --> 00:03:14.459
As graceful as a swan,

00:03:14.460 --> 00:03:15.945
as agile as a dragon.

00:03:16.339 --> 00:03:18.020
They are all exceptionally talented.

00:03:18.499 --> 00:03:19.580
Very good.

00:03:21.379 --> 00:03:24.058
It is because the
entertainment districts of Lin'an City

00:03:24.059 --> 00:03:25.780
are flourishing

00:03:25.900 --> 00:03:28.379
that these performers
have such bright futures.

00:03:29.325 --> 00:03:30.874
The rumors about Shengtang Guild

00:03:30.875 --> 00:03:33.195
were completely fabricated.

00:03:33.460 --> 00:03:36.299
It was merely
Gu Chengye playing power games

00:03:36.300 --> 00:03:37.859
and making wild accusations.

00:03:37.860 --> 00:03:40.460
Don't you agree, Your Majesty?

00:03:43.250 --> 00:03:45.010
You are right, Mother.

00:03:59.700 --> 00:04:02.060
Why are they performing
the Battle Formation Dance?

00:04:17.739 --> 00:04:19.298
I, Song Zhiyun, a humble commoner,

00:04:19.299 --> 00:04:20.899
boldly implore Your Majesty

00:04:20.900 --> 00:04:24.139
to see the truth, severely punish
the Dowager Consort and Gao Deng,

00:04:24.140 --> 00:04:25.720
thoroughly investigate Shengtang Guild,

00:04:25.720 --> 00:04:27.539
and uphold justice
for all women in the world.

00:04:27.779 --> 00:04:30.459
- Please investigate Shengtang Guild
- Please investigate Shengtang Guild

00:04:30.460 --> 00:04:32.980
- and uphold justice for all women.
- and uphold justice for all women.

00:04:54.580 --> 00:04:57.218
The Dowager Consort's birthday
is in a few days.

00:04:57.219 --> 00:04:59.260
If your performance

00:04:59.562 --> 00:05:01.979
has even the slightest mishap,

00:05:02.075 --> 00:05:05.499
or if you say
a single word you shouldn't,

00:05:06.580 --> 00:05:08.979
you will pay for it with your lives.

00:05:15.500 --> 00:05:17.020
You were always close with her.

00:05:17.140 --> 00:05:17.940
Now that

00:05:18.219 --> 00:05:22.379
she has died so unjustly,
don't you want to do something for her?

00:05:22.380 --> 00:05:23.738
Song Zhiyun,

00:05:23.739 --> 00:05:25.299
it's actually you.

00:05:25.940 --> 00:05:27.539
You have the nerve to come here?

00:05:27.659 --> 00:05:29.098
If it wasn't for you,

00:05:29.099 --> 00:05:31.220
how would we
have ended up in this state?

00:05:32.140 --> 00:05:34.659
Huanyue House used to be so wonderful.

00:05:34.779 --> 00:05:35.699
It's all your fault.

00:05:35.700 --> 00:05:36.939
If not for you,

00:05:36.940 --> 00:05:38.619
she wouldn't have died.

00:05:38.779 --> 00:05:39.579
Is relying on men

00:05:39.580 --> 00:05:41.099
for survival in Huanyue House

00:05:41.700 --> 00:05:43.379
the "wonderful life" you speak of?

00:05:43.380 --> 00:05:44.978
Then, what can I do?

00:05:44.979 --> 00:05:46.778
I don't have your courage.

00:05:46.779 --> 00:05:48.899
I am just a lowly performer.

00:05:48.900 --> 00:05:51.220
If I'm lucky enough
to be chosen by some official,

00:05:51.339 --> 00:05:53.699
I could at most whisper in his ear
to help give her a decent burial.

00:05:53.700 --> 00:05:55.659
Without anyone to back me up,

00:05:56.739 --> 00:05:58.338
I would end up just like her,

00:05:58.339 --> 00:05:59.859
with my hands tied

00:05:59.979 --> 00:06:01.460
at everyone's mercy.

00:06:02.580 --> 00:06:03.778
If you don't fight,

00:06:03.779 --> 00:06:05.099
you'll be preyed upon,

00:06:05.460 --> 00:06:07.978
and you'll just
have to swallow all the bitterness.

00:06:07.979 --> 00:06:09.978
Only by fighting
can there be a way to live

00:06:09.979 --> 00:06:11.659
and a way to get justice for her.

00:06:17.380 --> 00:06:19.059
But if you do fight

00:06:19.380 --> 00:06:21.178
and stand up against injustice,

00:06:21.179 --> 00:06:22.780
even if you fail,

00:06:23.140 --> 00:06:25.059
at least you'll have given
yourself an answer.

00:06:36.739 --> 00:06:38.460
Expecting you to accept this immediately

00:06:38.739 --> 00:06:40.419
is asking a bit much.

00:06:41.099 --> 00:06:42.260
I won't force you.

00:06:42.739 --> 00:06:44.019
If you're unwilling,

00:06:44.020 --> 00:06:45.659
I will just find another way.

00:06:53.419 --> 00:06:54.659
Wait.

00:07:07.800 --> 00:07:08.580
This...

00:07:08.612 --> 00:07:10.270
This is actually "Rosy Cloud Makeup."

00:07:10.500 --> 00:07:11.978
Using blood as makeup

00:07:11.979 --> 00:07:13.259
on such a joyous day,

00:07:13.260 --> 00:07:15.419
isn't this
a deliberate affront to His Majesty?

00:07:15.659 --> 00:07:16.979
Indeed.

00:07:17.979 --> 00:07:19.940
Is there any solid evidence?

00:07:20.587 --> 00:07:21.708
Your Majesty.

00:07:23.659 --> 00:07:24.539
Your Majesty,

00:07:24.787 --> 00:07:27.040
this shrew is a wanted criminal.

00:07:27.040 --> 00:07:28.679
She trespassed into
the imperial palace at night,

00:07:28.679 --> 00:07:31.179
and now she's using sweet words
to present forged evidence.

00:07:31.219 --> 00:07:32.859
Please, Your Majesty, see through her.

00:07:33.099 --> 00:07:35.179
Of course, there is solid evidence.

00:07:44.020 --> 00:07:47.380
Your Majesty, I wish to accuse
the Dowager Consort and Grand Commandant Gao

00:07:47.700 --> 00:07:48.940
of secret collusion.

00:07:49.020 --> 00:07:51.579
Under the guise of
the Shengtang Guild's courtesan queens,

00:07:51.580 --> 00:07:54.298
they secretly controlled
the city's entertainment districts,

00:07:54.299 --> 00:07:56.040
engaging in the trafficking
of female performers,

00:07:56.040 --> 00:07:58.539
treating human lives as worthless,
and conducting sex-for-power deals.

00:07:58.820 --> 00:08:01.099
According to my investigation,
over the years,

00:08:01.140 --> 00:08:03.820
44 women have died
tragically for no reason,

00:08:03.979 --> 00:08:05.580
and 75 have gone missing.

00:08:05.900 --> 00:08:08.460
Their miserable plight
is truly appalling.

00:08:09.580 --> 00:08:11.059
Furthermore,

00:08:11.060 --> 00:08:13.845
I have found evidence that
Dowager Consort is suspected of treason.

00:08:14.060 --> 00:08:16.340
Her ambition is immense
and must be guarded against.

00:08:18.299 --> 00:08:20.419
I have three pieces of evidence

00:08:21.060 --> 00:08:23.220
that can prove my words.

00:08:36.620 --> 00:08:38.739
This Beauty Portrait portrays

00:08:38.900 --> 00:08:41.899
the courtesan queens selected
by Shengtang Guild over the years.

00:08:42.500 --> 00:08:44.899
They have either passed away

00:08:45.299 --> 00:08:46.818
or their whereabouts are unknown.

00:08:46.819 --> 00:08:48.339
All of this was caused by the crimes

00:08:48.340 --> 00:08:51.058
of the Dowager Consort,
Grand Commandant Gao, and so on.

00:08:51.059 --> 00:08:53.580
And this ledger records

00:08:53.900 --> 00:08:57.220
all the officials, merchants,

00:08:57.459 --> 00:08:59.282
and establishments
involved in these crimes.

00:08:59.419 --> 00:09:01.979
Grand Commandant Gao Deng's name
is clearly listed.

00:09:02.380 --> 00:09:03.699
And this Jade Ruyi

00:09:03.700 --> 00:09:05.705
is a personal possession
of the Dowager Consort.

00:09:05.819 --> 00:09:07.778
It is undeniable physical evidence.

00:09:07.779 --> 00:09:09.219
With these three combined,

00:09:09.220 --> 00:09:10.899
the evidence is irrefutable.

00:09:11.059 --> 00:09:12.324
I ask Your Majesty

00:09:12.325 --> 00:09:13.979
to see the truth.

00:09:14.059 --> 00:09:16.619
Gu Chengye, you're talking nonsense!

00:09:18.579 --> 00:09:19.739
Mother.

00:09:21.500 --> 00:09:22.820
Gao Deng.

00:09:25.150 --> 00:09:26.708
The evidence is solid.

00:09:26.709 --> 00:09:28.682
How do you explain yourselves?

00:09:31.179 --> 00:09:32.580
Your Majesty.

00:09:34.337 --> 00:09:36.577
I was also deceived by Gao Deng.

00:09:37.020 --> 00:09:39.379
Even though Gao Deng is my nephew,

00:09:39.380 --> 00:09:42.019
he committed such a massive crime

00:09:42.220 --> 00:09:44.578
and even schemed against me.

00:09:44.579 --> 00:09:46.700
You must punish him severely

00:09:46.819 --> 00:09:48.660
as a warning to others.

00:09:52.200 --> 00:09:53.363
Aunt,

00:09:53.819 --> 00:09:55.779
since you are so heartless,

00:09:55.980 --> 00:09:58.379
don't blame me for turning on you.

00:10:00.179 --> 00:10:01.180
Your Majesty,

00:10:01.539 --> 00:10:02.938
everything I did

00:10:02.939 --> 00:10:04.619
was on her orders!

00:10:04.980 --> 00:10:07.859
She was resentful that the late Emperor
chose Your Majesty as the heir.

00:10:07.860 --> 00:10:09.379
She has always held a grudge.

00:10:09.500 --> 00:10:11.219
She had me use Shengtang Guild's name

00:10:11.220 --> 00:10:12.859
to win over and control officials.

00:10:12.860 --> 00:10:14.298
She was waiting for the right moment

00:10:14.299 --> 00:10:16.619
to install her son, King Gong,

00:10:16.620 --> 00:10:18.379
and usurp the throne!

00:10:26.500 --> 00:10:27.739
Your Majesty,

00:10:27.819 --> 00:10:29.899
don't listen to his lies.

00:10:29.980 --> 00:10:32.499
I have never had
any treasonous intentions.

00:10:33.020 --> 00:10:34.619
Fine.

00:10:35.860 --> 00:10:37.420
Fine!

00:10:38.220 --> 00:10:39.460
Mother,

00:10:40.100 --> 00:10:41.432
you and Gao Deng

00:10:41.699 --> 00:10:43.379
formed a faction for selfish ends

00:10:43.779 --> 00:10:45.580
and harmed the innocent.

00:10:46.100 --> 00:10:47.259
I order you

00:10:47.500 --> 00:10:49.658
to spend your life
in religious solitude.

00:10:49.659 --> 00:10:51.899
You are never to leave that place.

00:10:51.900 --> 00:10:56.060
King Gong shall be
punished along with you.

00:10:57.260 --> 00:10:58.420
Guards,

00:10:58.500 --> 00:10:59.779
take Dowager Consort

00:11:00.620 --> 00:11:01.578
away.

00:11:01.579 --> 00:11:03.779
No, Your Majesty!

00:11:03.860 --> 00:11:05.178
Your Majesty, listen to me.

00:11:05.179 --> 00:11:07.220
I was wrong!

00:11:07.419 --> 00:11:09.698
Please don't punish
my son, Your Majesty!

00:11:09.699 --> 00:11:11.099
Your Majesty!

00:11:11.100 --> 00:11:12.220
Gao Deng,

00:11:12.659 --> 00:11:14.340
your crimes are heinous.

00:11:15.059 --> 00:11:16.818
Take him to the dungeon immediately.

00:11:16.819 --> 00:11:19.580
Tomorrow at the third quarter
of the Wu hour, he will be executed.

00:11:22.179 --> 00:11:23.195
Don't move!

00:11:25.419 --> 00:11:26.280
Stand back!

00:11:26.280 --> 00:11:27.820
Gao Deng, have you lost your mind?

00:11:27.939 --> 00:11:29.058
Let me out of the city.

00:11:29.059 --> 00:11:30.379
Tell them to stand back,

00:11:30.500 --> 00:11:32.460
or I'll die with you.

00:11:33.659 --> 00:11:34.499
Stand back!

00:11:37.537 --> 00:11:39.069
Escort His Majesty out first.

00:11:43.260 --> 00:11:45.099
You...

00:11:57.500 --> 00:11:58.739
I never thought

00:11:58.740 --> 00:12:00.300
that I, Gao Deng,

00:12:00.539 --> 00:12:01.979
would die

00:12:02.459 --> 00:12:04.300
at your hands.

00:12:06.500 --> 00:12:07.460
This stab

00:12:07.819 --> 00:12:09.619
is for Liu Ruyan.

00:12:11.100 --> 00:12:12.259
This stab

00:12:12.459 --> 00:12:14.379
is for Shangguan Yu.

00:12:15.579 --> 00:12:16.859
This stab

00:12:17.699 --> 00:12:20.107
is for all the
female performers in the world.

00:12:32.500 --> 00:12:35.019
It's over now. It's okay.

00:12:35.699 --> 00:12:37.180
He is dead.

00:12:37.699 --> 00:12:39.180
He can't do any more harm.

00:12:46.837 --> 00:12:50.657
♪Even if I drift
within a darkened whirl♪

00:12:50.762 --> 00:12:54.374
♪Kindred souls
meet the light and become one♪

00:12:54.375 --> 00:13:02.270
♪So many chapters,
every wound remembered♪

00:13:02.337 --> 00:13:06.399
♪Back where we once stood,
the blossoms still remain♪

00:13:06.400 --> 00:13:09.482
♪The night runs deep like watching eyes♪

00:13:09.700 --> 00:13:11.745
♪Wave after wave of sorrow♪